There was so much going on this day! I was super exhausted and running low on energy! I wasn’t feeling cute or in my zone! But I knew I had to put that aside and get the damn job done! There were times where I wanted to just give up and not do it. I couldn’t get the vision I had in my head for this video out on camera! I’ve learned that not all my videos will come out the way I want them to and it’s up to me to make the most out of it and still have fun doing it!  Thank you to my bestfriend for always being patient with me and keeping me inspired! @dittoengurelli  you’re the best

Ps there were soooo many people this day recording us lol 😂 it was kinda hard to focus 🧘‍♀️
